data.description: Well-maintained cozy cottage style home, 3 bedrooms and 1 bath in a quiet neighborhood.  Full basement with finished bedroom for added living space and storage.  All new insulated windows, high efficiency furnace/AC and appliances with a bonus of a 4.8KW solar system with 12 panels  to reduce your energy bills every year. A fully fenced in yard with patio area will make for enjoyable outside living. Desirable location, providing quick access to local amenities including downtown shopping, restaurants, marinas, Cartier Park, Lincoln Lake and the beautiful sand beaches of Lake Michigan at Stearns Park. Whether you are looking for a cute vacation home, convenient Air B&B location, or just a new home close to the lake, this is the home for you!
